DST.F.summary: Storytel AB (publ) provides audiobooks and e-books streaming services. It operates in two segments, Streaming and Publishing. The company offers a subscription service for audiobooks and e-books under the Storytel, Mofibo, Kitab Sawti, and iCast brands. It also publishes audiobooks primarily through the publisher, Storyside. In addition, the company provides book imprints through Norstedts, Printz Publishing, RabÃ©n & SjÃ¶gren, B. WahlstrÃ¶ms, the Danish publisher People's publishing houses, as well as Gummerus, Norstedts Kartor, and book clubs. It operates in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, the Netherlands, Poland, Belgium, Germany, Finland, Russia, South Korea, Singapore, Thailand, India, the United Arab Emirates, Israel, Turkey, Bulgaria, Spain, Italy, Iceland, Brazil, Mexico, and Colombia. Storytel AB (publ) is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
